for group_name, df_group in reversed(tuple(df.groupby(pd.Grouper(key='timestamp', freq='d')))):
    
    if not df_group.empty:
        print("Plot for day:", group_name.strftime('%d %B %Y'))
        fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(15,10))
        
        df_group.plot(kind='line',x='timestamp',y='count', figsize=(15,10), grid=True, ax=ax)

        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(dates.HourLocator())
        ax.xaxis.set_major_formatter(dates.DateFormatter('%H:%M'))


        plt.show()
